## 📋 Requirements

### 🔧 Hardware Requirements
- ESP32 / Arduino Microcontroller  
- Motor Driver Module (L298N / L293D)  
- DC Motors (2 or 4 depending on chassis)  
- Robot Car Chassis with Wheels  
- Camera Module (ESP32-CAM / USB Camera)  
- Battery Pack (Li-ion / Li-Po)  
- Voltage Regulator (if required)  
- Jumper Wires  
- Breadboard / Custom PCB (optional)  

---

### 💻 Software Requirements
- Arduino IDE  
- ESP32 / Arduino Board Package  
- Required Libraries:
  - WiFi.h (for wireless control)
  - BluetoothSerial.h (optional)
  - ESP32-CAM libraries (for video streaming)
- Serial Monitor (for debugging)

---

### ⚙️ System Requirements
- Laptop / PC for programming  
- USB Cable for uploading code  
- Stable Wi-Fi connection (for video streaming)  
- Mobile / Web Interface for control  

---

### 🌐 Optional Requirements (Advanced Features)
- Mobile App for remote control  
- Web dashboard for live streaming  
- GPS Module (for tracking)  
- Ultrasonic Sensor (for obstacle avoidance)  
- AI modules (for object detection)  
